{"tid":1287572,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不能忘記死士同大家講嘅說話","createTime":"2019-07-05T09:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T09:13:16.000Z","uid":18648,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3512ab20eb8b81d9ba272b07ec65723868369c93","tid":1287572,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:10:55.000Z","msg":"雖然我睇左好多次<br />\n聽到已經識背<br />\n但每次睇都眼泛淚光<br />\n<br />\n死士為大家付出一切<br />\n甚至想為大家擋子彈<br />\n我地無理由連聽都唔聽佢地嘅說話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/K0EmC0VOdzI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FK0EmC0VOdzI&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BHjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=b9d20106\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/K0EmC0VOdzI</a><br />\n「唉！唉！希望你地好運喇，老豆比唔到d咩你，你地睇下老豆今日做d咩，睇下會唔會對你嘅人生有d參考？對與錯我唔夠膽講，我驚你媽話我教錯你地，但你地成熟咗喇，有自己嘅個人思想，你地自己諗下喇。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2-vlnto9gzI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2-vlnto9gzI&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BHjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=fe100ed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2-vlnto9gzI</a><br />\n「我除低口罩係因為想比大家知道，其實我地香港人真係無得再輸，我地香港人真係唔可以再輸，再輸，係十年你諗住十年我地公民社會就會一沉百踩。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190703/s00001/1562091762662/示威者-闖立會為展對抗政府決心-闖入者深明會入獄-哭說「最擔心母親」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190703%2Fs00001%2F1562091762662%2F%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E9%97%96%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E7%82%BA%E5%B1%95%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B1%BA%E5%BF%83-%E9%97%96%E5%85%A5%E8%80%85%E6%B7%B1%E6%98%8E%E6%9C%83%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84-%E5%93%AD%E8%AA%AA%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%80%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E3%80%8D&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BHjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=2c2b3457\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190703%2Fs00001%2F1562091762662%2F%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E9%97%96%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E7%82%BA%E5%B1%95%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B1%BA%E5%BF%83-%E9%97%96%E5%85%A5%E8%80%85%E6%B7%B1%E6%98%8E%E6%9C%83%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84-%E5%93%AD%E8%AA%AA%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%80%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E3%80%8D&h=f70d1a6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190703/s00001/1562091762662/示威者-闖立會為展對抗政府決心-闖入者深明會入獄-哭說「最擔心母親」</a><br />\n王奇 奧運 等等...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後我想同返義士們死士們講<br />\n你地有難<br />\n我地一定會幫你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定會籌錢比你地<br />\n做生活費 律師費 等等.....<br />\n唔好再諗做烈士<br />\n我地講過 齊上齊落<br />\n一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c7d7696b1211911dac9f36429dafcc1bd2d6a2d4","tid":1287572,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rhjMbT4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrhjMbT4.png&h=53408b2c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}